## Resources

- [choosealicense.com](https://choosealicense.com/) -- Simple license comparison tool
- [OSI Approved Licenses](https://opensource.org/licenses/) -- Full list of OSI-approved licenses
- [SPDX License List](https://spdx.org/licenses/) -- Standard license identifiers
- [tl;drLegal](https://tldrlegal.com/) -- Plain-language license summaries
